title: Taco Bell Party
description:
Written by Jon Bershad

Starring Dan Hodapp, Jonathan Marballi, Langan Kingsley, Kelly Hudson, Avery Monsen.

Directed by John Flynn.

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, August 13, 2012.

Filmed by Alex Aden.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
